# Prompt评估 API测试
@promptUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/prompt

@taskId = 6
@evalId = 3

### Get All Tasks
GET {{promptUrl}}/task

## response:
# [{
#   "taskName": "更新后的任务名",
#   "taskId": 5
# }]

### Create Task
POST {{promptUrl}}/task
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskName": "测试任务"
}

### no response

### Update Task Name
PUT {{promptUrl}}/task/{{taskId}}?task_name=更新后的任务

### no response

### Delete Task
DELETE {{promptUrl}}/task/{{taskId}}

### response:
# {
#   "message": "Task deleted successfully"
# }

### Get Task by ID
GET {{promptUrl}}/task/{{taskId}}

## response:
# {
#   "taskName": "测试任务",
#   "taskId": 6
# }

### Get Task Evals
